---
import Site from '../layouts/Site.astro';
---

<Site
  title="FAQ"
  description="Frequently asked questions about staying at The Owl's Nest."
>
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container" style="max-width: 720px;">
      <h1>FAQ</h1>
      <p>
        Frequently asked questions — coming soon. The full list will land in
        Phase 3 alongside the blog and area guide. A couple of placeholder
        answers below in the meantime.
      </p>

      <h2>What time is check-in and check-out?</h2>
      <p>
        Check-in is at 4:00 PM and check-out is at 11:00 AM. <em>(Placeholder —
        confirm against your booking confirmation, which is the source of
        truth.)</em>
      </p>

      <h2>Are pets allowed?</h2>
      <p>
        No — we don't allow pets at the property. <em>(Placeholder — full pet
        policy will be documented here in Phase 3.)</em>
      </p>

      <p>
        For anything not covered, get in touch via the <a href="/book">Book</a>
        page and we'll reply by email.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</Site>
